<div  class="x-text none"   >
<h4  class="h-custom-headline t-responsive center-text h4" ><span><span style="color: #ffffff;">JOIN THE VALUECENTRIC TEAM!</span></span></h4></div><hr  class="x-gap" style="margin: 50px 0 0 0;"><a id="careers-button" class="x-btn x-btn-x-large"  href="#x-section-5"  target="_blank"   data-options="thumbnail: ''"><i  class="x-icon x-icon-group"  data-x-icon="&#xf0c0;" aria-hidden="true"></i>BROWSE ALL POSITIONS</a></div></div></div><div id="x-section-2" class="x-section" style=" margin: 0px; padding: 40px 0px 110px; background-color: #ffffff;" ><div  class="x-container max width" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 30px 0px 0px; "><div  class="x-column x-sm x-1-1" style="padding: 0px 30px; "  >
<div  class="x-text none"   >
<h4  class="h-custom-headline responsive-heading center-text h4" ><span><span style="color: #dc291e;">Creativity, Curiosity, Commitment</span></span></h4><span id="x-responsive-text-1" data-x-element="responsive_text" data-x-params="{&quot;selector&quot;:&quot;.responsive-heading&quot;,&quot;compression&quot;:&quot;1.0&quot;,&quot;minFontSize&quot;:&quot;33pt&quot;,&quot;maxFontSize&quot;:&quot;48pt&quot;}"></span>
<p style="text-align: center; font-size: 14pt;"><span style="color: #000000;">ValueCentric is an exciting software company that delivers a web-based data management and analytics platform for pharmaceutical and medical device industries. We are a rapidly growing company with no shortage of opportunities for talented individuals. If you thrive in a dynamic, forward thinking environment we’d love to hear from you.</span></p>
</div></div></div></div><div id="x-section-3" class="x-section" style=" margin: 0px; padding: 45px 0px 0px; background-color: transparent;" ><div  class="x-container max width" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; "><div  class="x-column x-sm x-1-1" style="padding: 0px; "  >
